# Gamified XAI (Kantian + Utilitarian) — COFFEE Scenarios

> Synthetic, reproducible stimuli and scripts for a four-condition study (no explanation / Kantian / utilitarian / combined+meta) on ethically-aware consumer choices.

**Tested on:** Windows 11 / Python 3.11 · **No human subjects** (simulation only)

## Quickstart (Artifact)

### Windows (PowerShell)
```powershell
python -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
pip install -r requirements.txt
python scripts/run_experiment.py --config stimuli/experiment_config.yml
python scripts/run_conditions.py --delta-util 0.22 --delta-frac 0.33
python scripts/make_condition_plots.py
python scripts/make_poster_text.py
python scripts/make_poster_table.py
streamlit run app.py

